seo: Joomla,远程命令执行漏洞,CVE-2020-11890,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测Joomla系统中的远程命令执行漏洞（CVE-2020-11890），通过构造特定请求判断是否存在漏洞并输出结果。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the remote command execution vulnerability (CVE-2020-11890) in the Joomla system by constructing specific requests to determine if the vulnerability exists and output the results.
